[node name="Label" type="Label" parent="HelpTextCanvas/HelpPanel/VBoxContainer"]
layout_mode = 2
text = "Earth is struggling, so it sent YOU and your crew to colonize new planets!
You arived on a planet that has been given name Enyo and you have to set up big enough colony so that there can be a basic infrastructure 
and a masive transport of people from Earth can begin
Right as you arrived, you noticed signs of life and one of your crew members got eaten by an unknown animal!
You must deffend your base from these aliens and not let another life go in vain."

[node name="Label3" type="Label" parent="HelpTextCanvas/HelpPanel/VBoxContainer"]
