[node name="Label4" type="Label" parent="HelpTextCanvas/HelpPanel/VBoxContainer"]
layout_mode = 2
text = "You can build multiple buildings, each serves it purpose and you wont be able to make it on the planet without having multiple of each!

HOUSE - Server as an accomodation for your colonists. 
each house can accomodate 10 people and new built houses are filled with new colonist just after the day ends. 
Watch out! - new colonists wont move in, if you dont have enough farms! The ratio must always be 1 farm to 2 houses.

MINE - Extracts useful resources from the planets mountains. After each day, you get 15 minerals
Watch out! - Mines can be built only on tiles around the tile with a mineral icon

FARM - Produces food for you colonists
Watch out! - There always has to be enough farms to support your houses

Generator - These generator are can only produce energy during the night, so after you end a day, next day you will be able to 
use the energy that was stored in the bateries

ARTILLERY - This is, for now, your only line of defense against the aliens. 
Once you built an artillery, you will be able to take down those pesky aliens!


SHOOTING
Unlocked once artillery is built. 
Aliens move constantly, but we get only a glimpse of their last position during the sunset, when the remaining sun ilumnates their antenas for
a while, before they go dark again. That means, that you have to observe the aliens position, figure out the pattern and always plan your 
shot in advance! If the alien moves during the night to the same location you mark to be shot at during the day, the alien will be eliminated
The number of shots you can prepare is determined by the number of turrets
Watch out! - Aliens always move towards you rocket ship and will destroy everything building that crosses their path\""

